Sync All
Create Both
Expunge Both

IMAPAccount Personal
Host imap.gmail.com
User tom.auty@gmail.com
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
PassCmd "gpg --batch --yes --quiet --no-tty --decrypt ~/.mutt/auth/.msmtp-work.gpg"

IMAPStore Personal-remote
Account Personal

MaildirStore Personal-local
Path ~/Mail/Personal/
Inbox ~/Mail/Personal/INBOX

Channel Personal-inbox
Master ":Personal-remote:INBOX"
Slave ":Personal-local:INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel Personal-archive
Master ":Personal-remote:[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave ":Personal-local:archive"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel Personal-sent
Master ":Personal-remote:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave ":Personal-local:sent"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel Personal-drafts
Master ":Personal-remote:[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave ":Personal-local:drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *


